  <brief_title>The Efficacy of Three Months-prednisolone Therapy for Chronic Eosinophilic Pneumonia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 4, Randomized Study of Three Months-prednisolone Therapy in the Treatment of Chronic Eosinophilic Pneumonia</official_title>
